headline: Stanley Black & Decker: This Dividend King Is Worth Holding After Q4 Results (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Stanley Black & Decker delivered solid Q4 results, beating EPS estimates despite headwinds, with a focus on debt reduction. Learn why SWK is downgraded to hold.
